verbose_text: XREF_BIBR Investigation of the Protein Databank model of NDUFA6 (PDB : 5XTD.E) confirms that the proximity of the Arg64 residue to critical residues of NDUFAB1 could inhibit binding of NDUFAB1 when mutated (XREF_FIG B).
